Commands to run this repo 

1. go to 01_vpc
2. terraform init (or) terraform init -reconfigure
3. terrafrom plan
4. terraform apply -auto-approve
5. terraform destroy -auto-approve

then go to 02_sg and run same commands 


To destroy all the resources from 14_payment folder to 01_vpc
for i in `ls -dr */` ; do cd $i ; terraform destroy -auto-approve ; cd .. ; done

ls -dr */  - this command will list the directories in reverse order.

